<project xml:id="cool-conectaUnDiagramaConUnAlgoritmo" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"> 

<title>Conecta un diagrama con un algoritmo</title>

<statement>
  <p>Explica cómo el diagrama corresponde al algoritmo.</p>
  <image source="svg-source/tikz-file-136398">
      <shortdescription>Diagrama de resta con bloques en base diez.</shortdescription></image>
  <image source="svg-source/tikz-file-151059">
      <shortdescription>Resta por valor posicional.</shortdescription></image>
</statement>

<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>Sample response: I can see that there are 3 hundreds, 8 tens, and 2 ones, but one of the tens has been moved over to get more ones. In the algorithm, the 80 and 2 are crossed out to show this. The blocks that are not crossed out show the <m>100 + 10 + 5</m> in the algorithm.</p>
  </solution>


